        "when": "2026-06",
        "text": "We have twice had Hannah take our family photos, and are twice delighted! I highly recommend Hannah for any upcoming photo needs you have. She's communicative, has amazing options for your shoot, is thoroughly professional and the finished product is top notch."
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2020-07",
        "text": "Hannah is amazing! She shot my surprise engagement and she did a family photo shoot for us with our dogs (including a young puppy). She is professional and does an amazing job keeping you comfortable and allowing the moments to be intimate. You barely even know she's there! She is patient with both humans and dogs, and can see the shot before you even sit where she asks you to. Hannah's editing is also perfect and well worth the short wait to get your photos back!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2023-11",
        "text": "Hannah is the BEST! She has taken our family photos 3 years in a row now, and does an amazing job every time. She is patient with my crazy crew of 3 kiddos, takes her time every time, and delivers beautifully edited photos. 10/10 recommend!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2022-11",
        "text": "Hannah photographed our wedding ceremony at the Jeffco courthouse. Hannah is amazing to work with and we are so happy with the pictures!! She made us feel very comfortable and we had so much fun when we did our couples shots at Red Rocks. Highly recommend!!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2022-08",
        "text": "I can’t say enough good things about Hannah. We we’re screwed over by our previous maternity photographer and Hannah offered to do a complimentary mini session to make up for someone else. However, our little baby decided to make her appearance 5 weeks early and before the session. A week after we got home Hannah came to our house and took the most amazing moment. These photos will be cherished forever."
